{"tid":2416490,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國靚媽丨全智賢露纖腰晒少女味 金泰希扁嘴賣萌","createTime":"2021-02-21T05:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T06:14:15.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8a0d280a9c6166cc776d5916c536b37e4e3fa197","tid":2416490,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T05:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Qe9rfIxWeP1RV0XqtwxDfkgnqS8=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7VO45WKHEFCSPGP6AXTHS4DDV4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQe9rfIxWeP1RV0XqtwxDfkgnqS8%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7VO45WKHEFCSPGP6AXTHS4DDV4.jpg&h=9e003706&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年39歲的韓國女神全智賢入行24年，即使已為兩子之母依然人氣不減，加上她生B後積極修身，狀態弗爆的她深受廣告商歡迎，代言多個品牌搵真銀。近日再有全智賢代言的新相公開，照片中她紮起頭髮，穿上寬鬆的悠閒服低調晒纖腰，再配上淡妝及甜美笑容，充滿少女味。<br />\n<br />\n密密搵真銀<br />\n而韓國另一靚媽、40歲的金泰希近期亦密密拍廣告搵真銀，為代言的服裝品牌拍攝春季海報，而金泰希的事務所日前就公開多張花絮照。當日金泰希於拍攝現場換上多套西裝及長裙，分別示範優雅、型格等不同風格，而已經40歲的金泰希於鏡頭後不時扁嘴賣萌，展示可愛一面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sNwPAgL-femubDAof9JpNRaoyVU=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DSQDJY5JYJCERMPIWWPF42LL6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsNwPAgL-femubDAof9JpNRaoyVU%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDSQDJY5JYJCERMPIWWPF42LL6E.jpg&h=71fff960&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vE5aBjVXTLZVzJKa3MdB-HFETtE=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BU7UFS4JUJGYJGH4CU4XWAYYDY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvE5aBjVXTLZVzJKa3MdB-HFETtE%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBU7UFS4JUJGYJGH4CU4XWAYYDY.jpg&h=8f32cdf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bVxJx8-wWGBuXxwWRjD3v0BvESY=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DK7SN2XWU5D57EPAIKIF6BSRQM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbVxJx8-wWGBuXxwWRjD3v0BvESY%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDK7SN2XWU5D57EPAIKIF6BSRQM.jpg&h=f6652b7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oFHbFUJOHSIuBneVSviR-U4fYRA=/802x1203/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HW7ICXNGLREJJGHGPENVU33I2Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoFHbFUJOHSIuBneVSviR-U4fYRA%3D%2F802x1203%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHW7ICXNGLREJJGHGPENVU33I2Y.jpg&h=7d1d23bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iziQZjq3gXA1XlsVbt0k_X6xdyg=/802x1203/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZLRQMLTBXNGXHKVKF2I7LBFENA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiziQZjq3gXA1XlsVbt0k_X6xdyg%3D%2F802x1203%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZLRQMLTBXNGXHKVKF2I7LBFENA.jpg&h=558b7adc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/F7HMwJXdPEXAVBvK26cTHEEqtAI=/802x1203/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PVJB522WKVFF3CYKXBQEWNNIFY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FF7HMwJXdPEXAVBvK26cTHEEqtAI%3D%2F802x1203%2Ffilters%3Aquality%2810